"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"gm all!\\n\\nI will focus the first edition of this weekly series for people brand new to web3 and confused about where to even start.\\n\\n## Top articles of the week\\n\\n* This [beginner’s guide](https://creatoreconomy.so/p/curious-beginner-guide-to-crypto?utm_source=pocket_mylist) to crypto from Peter Yang is an excellent introduction to web3. He explains blockchains, fungible and non-fungible tokens, Bitcoin, Ethereum, NFT’s & DAO’s in a very simple way. \\n* Once you have read the [BTC](https://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf) and [ETH](https://ethereum.org/en/whitepaper/) white papers and the beginner’s guide above and are ready to go a little deeper, this [breakdown for ETH](https://www.notboring.co/p/own-the-internet?utm_source=pocket_mylist) from Packy is great. It is a very in depth bull case for ETH (38 minute read!)\\n* Now that you have a bit more background on blockchains, tokens (fungible and non-fungible), this is a natural transition to this next article from Chris Dixon about the [idea of a 1000 true fans and NFT’s](https://cdixon.org/2021/02/27/NFTs-and-a-thousand-true-fans).\\n\\n## Tweet of the week + follow recommendation\\n\\nThis thread from Yash recommends some of the things you can start doing in web3 to get comfortable with the tools, wallets, and platforms.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/yb_effect/status/1458569764637454347?s=20](https://twitter.com/yb_effect/status/1458569764637454347?s=20)\\n\\nChris Dixon is a partner at a16z and invests in web3 projects. His tweets are insightful for anyone trying to get into a deeper crypto rabbit hole and Chris also writes on his blog [here](https://cdixon.org/).\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/cdixon?s=20](https://twitter.com/cdixon?s=20)\\n\\nThis should be a good start for anyone looking to dip their toes in web3!\\n\\nwagmi!\",\"timestamp\":1636931348,\"title\":\"Wtf is web3?!\"},\"digest\":\"oo4a24b78sC1t8okckm_2bxwQYwel8yVb35UxnYkRKY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xbacDA1e925bCaa679539A5D650111e4a50a651D4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZmeSqAOpuAFSBEUeXtwwaKEnDPrsI6SnKqiMWMXX1wc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hxDrF39nKMoXda53Q_ccX40We_5hmLvjZQZNKvv8x8c\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"cYcerabN9cODtsAHte3qizQg0U_JZ9VlwG_z6wAaIFGAX4PDOnJ2YKtCXwW5it8jUsdv3g9o6yj0ehAwNjlrsw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x27d18a4295c539bf5c51aaaa2720163d72945fc38452a7ac562e17067d074abc688ccbda0f538523013e0af7516629cd58fda66585b0e3e28b85fc675efbf33f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZmeSqAOpuAFSBEUeXtwwaKEnDPrsI6SnKqiMWMXX1wc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hxDrF39nKMoXda53Q_ccX40We_5hmLvjZQZNKvv8x8c\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"zYz6FYyvZ-FGRWVsYq9yur978nrGjlzk09iwC8hvX2o\"}"